      "text": "<p>Trebalo bi da kreirate new <code>div</code> unutar vašeg <code>body</code> elementa.</p>",
      "testString": "const divs = [...document.querySelector('body')?.children].filter(child => child?.localName === 'div');\nassert.lengthOf(divs, 1);"
