      "text": "<p>Vaši šest <code>span</code> elementa unutar <code>.wheel</code> element trebalo bi da imaju <code>class</code> od <code>line</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "const spans = [...document.querySelectorAll('.wheel span')];\nassert.isTrue(spans?.every(span => span?.classList?.contains('line')));\nassert.lengthOf(document.querySelectorAll('.line'), 6);"
